nodes.text: Tynes was a male Human commander of the Sith Empire stationed on Korriban around 3643 BBY, when he was killed.

Tynes appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic as a Champion boss on Korriban. He is not directly involved in any quests, but can be killed for loot and as part of the achievement. This article assumes 100% game completion, which means he was killed.
